sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist<br/>(Python Code)
    participant SDK as Kubeflow SDK<br/>(TrainerClient)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Controller as Trainer Controller<br/>(Watch Stream)
    participant Pod as Training Pod<br/>(GPU Worker)
    participant Metrics as In-Pod Metrics Server<br/>28080/TCP HTTP
    participant RHOAICtrl as RHOAI Controller
    participant S3 as S3-compatible Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over User,Controller: Flow 1: Create Training Job (Kubernetes Backend)
        User->>SDK: trainer.train(<br/>trainer=CustomTrainer/TransformersTrainer,<br/>backend=KubernetesBackendConfig)
        SDK->>K8sAPI: POST TrainJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token<br/>TLS 1.2+
        K8sAPI-->>SDK: TrainJob created
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event: TrainJob added
        Controller->>Pod: Create training pods<br/>(with injected code for RHAI trainers)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 235, 235)
        Note over Pod,S3: Flow 3: S3 Checkpoint Storage (TransformersTrainer)
        Pod->>S3: Download existing checkpoints<br/>(on_init_end, resume training)<br/>Auth: AWS IAM credentials<br/>from Data Connection secret
        S3-->>Pod: Checkpoint artifacts
        Note over Pod: Training executes...<br/>JIT checkpointing on SIGTERM<br/>LIFO upload queue
        Pod->>S3: Upload checkpoint<br/>(async background, per-rank markers)<br/>Auth: AWS IAM credentials
        S3-->>Pod: Upload confirmed
    end

    rect rgb(235, 255, 235)
        Note over Pod,RHOAICtrl: Flow 2: RHAI Progression Tracking
        Note over Pod,Metrics: RHAI trainer injects HTTP metrics<br/>server into training pod at startup
        Pod->>Metrics: Start metrics server<br/>bind 0.0.0.0:28080
        RHOAICtrl->>Metrics: GET / (poll metrics)<br/>HTTP 28080/TCP<br/>No auth, No encryption
        Metrics-->>RHOAICtrl: JSON: {step, epoch, loss, ETA}
        Pod->>Pod: Write /dev/termination-log<br/>(final metrics on exit)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over User,HFHub: Flow 4: Model/Dataset Download
        Pod->>HFHub: Download model/dataset<br/>storage_uri: hf://<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)<br/>TLS 1.2+
        HFHub-->>Pod: Model artifacts
    end

    rect rgb(240, 235, 255)
        Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 5: Job Status Monitoring
        User->>SDK: trainer.get(name)
        SDK->>K8sAPI: GET TrainJob<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>SDK: TrainJob status
        SDK-->>User: TrainJob object
        User->>SDK: trainer.get_logs(name)
        SDK->>K8sAPI: GET pods/log<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>SDK: Pod log stream
        SDK-->>User: Training logs
    end
